<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="joke-n">joke <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dʒəʊk/    美 /dʒoʊk/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>笑话；玩笑：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He has a habit of <strong>telling jokes</strong>. 
他喜欢讲笑话。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I don't want anyone to <strong>make a joke about</strong> me!
我不希望任何人开我的玩笑！</p><footer>译林⑥ – 1</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="a-practical-joke">a practical joke</h3>
<p>1.<strong>恶作剧</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="play-a-joke-jokes-on">play a joke / jokes on</h3>
<p>1.<strong>戏弄；拿……开玩笑：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They decided to play a joke on their father by hiding his glasses.
他们决定把父亲的银镜藏起来和他开个玩笑。</p></div></div>